    All Classes and Interfaces

    Class
    Description
    CustomException
    Represents a custom exception for the tournament application.
    IndividualTournament
    Represents a tournament where players compete individually.
    Main
    The main class for the tournament application.
    Match
    Represents a match between two participants in a tournament.
    MatchTournamentNameComparator
    Comparator for sorting matches by the name of their associated tournament.
    MixedTournament
    Represents a tournament that allows both individual and team participation.
    Participant
    Represents a participant in a tournament, which can be a player or a team.
    Player
    Represents a player participating in a tournament.
    PlayerRankingComparator
    Comparator for sorting players by ranking and name.
    Team
    Represents a team participating in a tournament.
    TeamRankingComparator
    Comparator for sorting teams by their average ranking in descending order.
    TeamTournament
    Represents a tournament where players compete in teams.
    Tournament
    Represents a tournament with a name, associated game, and prize.
    TournamentManager
    Manages tournaments, players, teams, and matches.
    TournamentNameComparator
    Comparator for sorting tournaments by name.
